item.title: CVE-2016-8923|2024-08-06T02:35:02.253Z -- ibm -- curam%20social%20program%20management
item.description: IBM Curam Social Program Management 5.2, 6.0, and 7.0 contains a vulnerability that would allow an authorized user to obtain sensitive information from the profile of a higher privileged user that they should not have access to. IBM X-Force ID: 118536.
